	<h2>The conference for digitalisation and sustainability</h2>

	<p>

	Bits &amp; Bäume 2022 covers topics at the intersection between the areas of sustainability and digitalisation. They range from interconnected mobility, the resource and energy consumption of digital devices, data sufficiency and cooperative platform economies to issues around smart energy 	grids and the tendency towards monopolisation in the digital economy.

